description: Morana`s Glalie battled against Cress`s Panpour in a match that would close the Striaton Gym if Cress lost. This was the second match as Chili`s Pansear had already lost. Cress`s Panpour didn`t prove to be that good against Morana`s Glalie as it was quickly defeated.
name: Onigohri (Drago)
